then I'm going to click on "Propose new file". Going this way around,

27
00:01:43.033 --> 00:01:47.466
we are effectively creating a pull request back into our master branch.

28
00:01:47.466 --> 00:01:51.166
In addition to the commit message we had before, we also have

29
00:01:51.166 --> 00:01:55.566
a pull request commit message and a comment to go along with it.

30
00:01:55.566 --> 00:01:59.366
So here I'm writing in Markdown syntax. I can preview it;

31
00:01:59.366 --> 00:02:02.133
you can see I have a heading and then two bullets.

32
00:02:02.133 --> 00:02:07.000
Once I'm happy with this commit message and the corresponding comment,

33
00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:09.200
